        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Leaping from a hiding place, you quickly attack your foe before retreating. You Stride or Step, then attempt a melee or ranged Strike against a creature. After your Strike, you Sneak away. None of the movement taken as part of this activity triggers reactions.",
